<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>搜索结果 - Star Online Shopping</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="/css/style.css">
    <style>
        .search-page {
            max-width: 1226px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .search-header {
            background: #fff;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .search-form {
            display: flex;
            gap: 10px;
            align-items: center;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }
        .search-input {
            flex: 1;
            height: 40px;
            padding: 0 15px;
            border: 2px solid #ddd;
            border-radius: 4px;
            font-size: 14px;
            transition: border-color 0.3s;
        }
        .search-input:focus {
            outline: none;
            border-color: #ff6700;
        }
        .search-btn {
            height: 44px;
            padding: 0 20px;
            background: #ff6700;
            color: white;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 4px;
            cursor: pointer;
            font-size: 14px;
            transition: background-color 0.3s;
        }
        .search-btn:hover {
            background: #e55a00;
        }
        .search-info {
            color: #666;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
        .products-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(280px, 1fr));
            gap: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        .product-card {
            background: white;
            border-radius: 8px;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
            transition: transform 0.3s, box-shadow 0.3s;
        }
        .product-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 4px 16px rgba(0,0,0,0.15);
        }
        .product-image {
            width: 100%;
            height: 200px;
            object-fit: cover;
        }
        .product-info {
            padding: 15px;
        }
        .product-name {
            font-size: 16px;
            font-weight: 500;
            color: #333;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
            line-height: 1.4;
        }
        .product-price {
            font-size: 18px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #ff6700;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
        }
        .product-link {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 8px 16px;
            background: #ff6700;
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 4px;
            font-size: 14px;
            transition: background-color 0.3s;
        }
        .product-link:hover {
            background: #e55a00;
            color: white;
        }
        .pagination {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 10px;
            margin-top: 30px;
        }
        .pagination a {
            padding: 10px 15px;
            background: white;
            color: #333;
            text-decoration: none;
            border: 1px solid #ddd;
            border-radius: 4px;
            transition: all 0.3s;
        }
        .pagination a:hover {
            background: #ff6700;
            color: white;
            border-color: #ff6700;
        }
        .pagination a.disabled {
            color: #ccc;
            cursor: not-allowed;
            pointer-events: none;
        }
        .no-results {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 60px 20px;
            color: #666;
        }
        .no-results h3 {
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            color: #333;
        }
        .back-home {
            display: inline-block;
            margin-top: 20px;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            background: #ff6700;
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 4px;
            transition: background-color 0.3s;
        }
        .back-home:hover {
            background: #e55a00;
            color: white;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="search-page">
        <div class="search-header">
            <form class="search-form" method="get" action="/products/all">
                <input type="text" name="keyword" class="search-input" placeholder="搜索商品..." value="<%= keyword %>">
                <button type="submit" class="search-btn">搜索</button>
            </form>
            <div class="search-info">
                <% if (keyword) { %>
                    搜索 "<%= keyword %>" 找到 <%= products.length %> 个结果
                <% } else { %>
                    显示所有商品
                <% } %>
            </div>
        </div>

        <% if (products.length > 0) { %>
            <div class="products-grid">
                <% products.forEach(product => { %>
                    <div class="product-card">
                        <img src="<%= product.image || '/image/default.png' %>" alt="<%= product.name %>" class="product-image">
                        <div class="product-info">
                            <h3 class="product-name"><%= product.name %></h3>
                            <div class="product-price">¥<%= product.price %></div>
                            <a href="/product/<%= product.id %>" class="product-link">查看详情</a>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                <% }); %>
            </div>

            <div class="pagination">
                <% if (page > 1) { %>
                    <a href="/products/all?page=<%= page - 1 %>&keyword=<%= keyword %>">上一页</a>
                <% } else { %>
                    <a href="#" class="disabled">上一页</a>
                <% } %>
                
                <span style="padding: 10px 15px; background: #ff6700; color: white; border-radius: 4px;">
                    第 <%= page %> 页
                </span>
                
                <% if (page < totalPages) { %>
                    <a href="/products/all?page=<%= page + 1 %>&keyword=<%= keyword %>">下一页</a>
                <% } else { %>
                    <a href="#" class="disabled">下一页</a>
                <% } %>
            </div>
        <% } else { %>
            <div class="no-results">
                <h3>未找到相关商品</h3>
                <p>抱歉，没有找到与 "<%= keyword %>" 相关的商品。</p>
                <p>建议：</p>
                <ul style="text-align: left; display: inline-block; margin-top: 10px;">
                    <li>检查拼写是否正确</li>
                    <li>尝试使用更通用的关键词</li>
                    <li>减少关键词数量</li>
                </ul>
                <a href="/homepage.html" class="back-home">返回首页</a>
            </div>
        <% } %>
    </div>
</body>
</html>